ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes, strongly recommend this course to any cs student.
I learned lots of important techniques on parallel compuating on this course. I highly recommend it to other students who found parallel computing useful in their research.
It is a challenging course, but one can learn a lot from it with some commitment. I highly recommend this course to my fellow students.
I would recommend this course to anyone who is interested in high performance computing. Just be aware there will be some serious programming assignments.
good hands-on skills in C and parallel programming
I would definitely recommend this class to another student.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I learned a lot from this course. Now I feel more confident at applying parallel computing technqiues to my research.
